dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading and spot heights. "57400 7-68." Maps in margin: [Location map] -- [Comparative size map] -- Population -- Economic activity -- Tribes. Map shows administrative and international boundaries, national and département capitals, two classes of railroads, surfaced and unsurfaced roads, crude oil and gas pipelines, principal and secondary ports, and three classes of populated places.
